Base Project: rjelbert/geiger_counter  
Original Author: JiangJie Zhang (cajoetech@qq.com)  
License: MIT

-----------------------------------
Version 1.3.1  (LATEST)
-----------------------------------

• Project renamed to **Parrot – People’s ARduino Radiation mOniTor**
  - All user-facing references updated (Serial banner, README, etc.)
  - Device ID updated to PARROT-001

• Licensing and attribution clarified:
  - Added MIT LICENSE file with copyright:
      (c) 2025 Steven Sheeley
  - Added NOTICE file acknowledging original work:
      rjelbert/geiger_counter (MIT License), JiangJie Zhang
