• No functional changes to firmware behaviour compared to v1.3.0.

-----------------------------------
Version 1.3.0
-----------------------------------

• Added **hardware watchdog timer (8 seconds)**  
  - Prevents hangs, auto-reset on failure  

• Added **reset cause detection** using MCUSR flags  
  - Reports POR, BOR, WDT, external reset etc.

• Added **Service Mode at boot**
  - Hold Display Button during power-up
  - OLED ON
  - Short log period (10s)
  - No radmon uploads
  - Ideal for on-pole maintenance

• Added **radiation safety bands**
  - LOW
  - NORMAL (20 - 40 CPM)
  - WARNING (≥100 CPM)
  - DANGER (≥275 CPM)

• Added **smart LED rules**
  - RED    = Sensor fault (3× zero CPM)
  - YELLOW = High internal temp or HTTP failure
  - GREEN  = All good

• Added **brown-out and reset logging at startup**

• Added **fail reason tracking**
  - DHCP, connect fail, HTTP fail

• Added **optional telemetry endpoint stub**
  - Disabled by default (STATUS_PING_ENABLE = 0)

• Display shows:
  - Status
  - Uptime
  - Last upload age
  - Temp, humidity
  - Fail reason
  - IP address

• EEPROM usage remains unchanged

-----------------------------------
